, 33, 33); font-family: Cambria, &quot;Cambria Math&quot;, stixgeneral, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, serif; hyphens: none; line-height: inherit; font-size: 20px;\\\">Candy\\u2014sugar confectionery and chocolate\\u2014is not a recent invention: the ancient Arabs, Chinese, and Egyptians candied fruits and nuts in honey, and the Aztecs made a chocolate drink from the bean of the cacao tree. Today, Americans gratify themselves with, on average, 5.4\\u2009kg of sugar candy and 6.5\\u2009kg of chocolate per person annually.<span style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; outline: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 15px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; top: -0.5em;\\\"><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov\\/pmc\\/articles\\/PMC28747\\/#B2\\\" rid=\\\"B2\\\" class=\\\" bibr popnode\\\" role=\\\"button\\\" aria-expanded=\\\"false\\\" aria-haspopup=\\\"true\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; outline-style: none; outline-width: initial; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(55, 111, 170); text-decoration-line: underline; cursor: pointer;\\\">2<\\/a><\\/span><\\/p><p id=\\\"__p4\\\" class=\\\"p\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; outline: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin-top: 20pt; margin-bottom: 20pt; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: Cambria, &quot;Cambria Math&quot;, stixgeneral, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, serif; hyphens: none; line-height: inherit; font-size: 20px;\\\">Since candy has existed for centuries, we surmised that it cannot be totally unhealthy. We decided to investigate whether candy consumption was associated with longevity.<\\/p>\",\"ar\":\"<p id=\\\"__p2\\\" class=\\\"p p-first\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; outline: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin-top: 20pt; margin-bottom: 20pt; hyphens: none; line-height: inherit;\\\"><font color=\\\"#212121\\\" face=\\\"Cambria, Cambria Math, stixgeneral, Times New Roman, Times, serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-siz